---
title: Chicken & Pepper Stromboli with Mozzarella & Marinara Sauce
description: If there’s one thing we can all agree on, it’s that pizza is precious. So precious, in fact, that sometimes you need to wrap it up tight to keep all those tasty toppings safe. Enter stromboli: the ultimate pizza roll. Pork sausage and bell pepper are mixed with a spicy Tuscan blend of seasonings and cream cheese for a rich filling, then layered over mozzarella and rolled up tight in pizza dough. Once it’s baked, sliced, and dunked in marinara, you can breathe a deep sigh of relief—your dinner is safe and sound!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-pepper-stromboli-87dc9fdf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-pepper-stromboli-63bef54b202a53bb6608adab-45a7bbab.pdf
cuisine: Italian
